{"tid":1636954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"塞車，冇車搭，投訴就叫佢地屌柒林鄭月娥","createTime":"2019-10-08T00:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T17:16:58.000Z","uid":43785,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"ca669f0f2c0af7bce69755df8a60a80b6971552c","tid":1636954,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:35:16.000Z","msg":"塞車，冇車搭，投訴就叫佢地屌柒林鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥遲遲不回應五大訴求， 刻意挑釁 示威者情緒， 一意孤行行王權緊急法，以及用 蒙面法 損害港人自由，港人迫不得意起義，攬炒是必須的。<br />\n<br />\n港人若對緊急法視若無睹，實在對自己，對下一代唔住。<br />\n<br />\n我地作為香港人，要明白示威者所做既野是為了大家，為了下一代，佢地冇做錯。<br />\n<br />\n我地應該反問林鄭月娥，點解唔回應五大訴求。點解要引用緊急法挑起群民眾情緒。"},{"pid":"e7b89c47c9733ffa88dd7afbffc07368faca7ddf","tid":1636954,"uid":34444,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:35:30.000Z","msg":"你點影的"},{"pid":"3a57429bc9ceb1b2ca444686caa50796688cd344","tid":1636954,"uid":35931,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:35:32.000Z","msg":"你點影的"},{"pid":"5929ab7a18330c325aec1beac979921a77d684fd","tid":1636954,"uid":133377,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:35:48.000Z","msg":"Yes sir"},{"pid":"d681b5187888bdc85f39754f7733c6d2353df891","tid":1636954,"uid":74973,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:35:49.000Z","msg":"Good morning sir!"},{"pid":"deaa089c45d1930ef1e3543ccd3090a9d0c1844e","tid":1636954,"uid":174191,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:35:55.000Z","msg":"sir"},{"pid":"303a2b4983702d67f823f07a86ac837a29b668d9","tid":1636954,"uid":199227,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HMsPeT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HMsPeT.png&h=3295436a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGood morning sir!"},{"pid":"f5a8934f30c56ed04370cf32b16709dd8aeeef8d","tid":1636954,"uid":163510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:3